INSTALL
=======

To install, run

    ./waf configure
    ./waf install

You can change installation prefix by adding --prefix=... option to
configure.

You can change destdir by adding --destdir=... option to install.

REQUIREMENTS
============

  * [GLib](http://www.gtk.org/) at least 2.20.0
  * [Vala](http://live.gnome.org/Vala) at least 0.7.7 (master newer than
    2009-09-23 before 0.7.7 is released)
  * [GOjbect-introspection](http://live.gnome.org/GObjectIntrospection) at
    least 0.6.5
  * [Python](http://www.python.org) (for compilation only) at least 2.3
